The '''1907 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their seventeenth ever season of organized football. Coached by [[C. S. Roller|Charles Roller]] (VMI class of 1901), the Keydets went 5-3.<ref name="VMI">http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf</ref>
